@afthunderbirds Major Jason Markzon, better known as @thunderbird.8, has arrived in Central Florida for a site visit ahead of their appearance headlining the @cocoabeachairshow scheduled for April 17-18. Our friend @mikekillianphotography was there to catch the shots & speak to him. Thanks again Flack, & thx to @45thspacewing for hosting us
.
.
.
